title: Harmonic position
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Two pairs of points $$\{A,B\},\{P,Q\}$$ in $$\Bbb R\mathrm P^1$$ are in //harmonic position// (or $$\{A,B\}$$ [[separates|Separation on the real projective line]] $$\{P,Q\}$$ //harmonically//) if

$$
\operatorname{cr}(A,P,B,Q)=-1.
$$